OL,3,CReporting Rome: Covering the funeral
OL,4,Cof Pope Francis
OL,6,FI watched Pope Francis give his Easter
OL,7,FBlessing - Urbi et Orbi - from the
OL,8,FVatican, on Easter Sunday. A short
OL,9,Ftime later, I witnessed him being
OL,10,Fdriven among the faithful, in St
OL,11,FPeter's Square.
OL,13,FI did not expect what happened next...
OL,14,FI was listening to the radio, just
OL,15,Fbefore nine, on Monday morning, when I
OL,16,Freceived a news alert on my phone.
OL,18,FOver the next few seconds, it was
OL,19,Ffollowed by many more pings. The Pope
OL,20,Fwas dead!
