OL,3,CReporting Rome: Covering the funeral
OL,4,Cof Pope Francis
OL,6,FEarlier this year, we had been
OL,7,Fexpecting the news, when the Pontiff
OL,8,Fwas in hospital. Though he looked and
OL,9,Fsounded frail on Sunday, we presumed
OL,10,Fthat he had pulled through.
OL,12,FThe death of Francis, a few hours
OL,13,Fafter the holiest day in the Christian
OL,14,Fcalendar was still a shock. I have no
OL,15,Fway of proving this, but I did wonder
OL,16,Fif the Pope had wished to live long
OL,17,Fenough, to witness the resurrection.
OL,18,FWe will never know this for sure, but
OL,19,Fa number of respected commentators
OL,20,Fhave shared the same view.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
