OL,3,CReporting Rome: Covering the funeral
OL,4,Cof Pope Francis
OL,6,FCameraman Tommy Hassan, and I, were
OL,7,Fdispatched to Rome early on Tuesday
OL,8,Fmorning. We were broadcasting live
OL,9,Fthat evening. The next five days were
OL,10,Fa roller-coaster, as we were caught up
OL,11,Fin a sea of humanity, which descended
OL,12,Fupon The Vatican.
OL,14,FAt one point, I had difficulty
OL,15,Fremembering which day it was. The
OL,16,Ffaithful came in their tens of
OL,17,Fthousands!
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
