OL,3,CReporting Rome: Covering the funeral
OL,4,Cof Pope Francis
OL,6,FThis wasn't my first Papal funeral.
OL,7,FExactly twenty years ago, in April
OL,8,F2005, I was in Rome for the Requiem of
OL,9,FJohn Paul II. I remember the emotion
OL,10,Ffollowing his death. First, he came
OL,11,Ffrom a very Catholic country. Poland
OL,12,Fwas a relatively short journey from
OL,13,FRome.
OL,15,FThey came... and, they came in their
OL,16,Fhundreds of thousands to mourn. What I
OL,17,Fnoticed most, was their ages. They
OL,18,Fwere young. So much for a Church which
OL,19,Fwas dying.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
