OL,3,CReporting Rome: Covering the funeral
OL,4,Cof Pope Francis
OL,6,FThis time, once again, I was struck by
OL,7,Fthe huge numbers of young people. Many
OL,8,Fof them had come to Rome because it
OL,9,Fwas the Jubilee of Teenagers; an event
OL,10,Fwhich drew tens of thousands from
OL,11,Faround the world. This event took
OL,12,Fplace, despite the death of Francis.
OL,14,FThese people may have come here on a
OL,15,Fpilgrimage. They remained as mourners.
OL,17,FLast Saturday morning, at the Pope's
OL,18,Ffuneral, the television cameras
OL,19,Frightly focussed on the Mass, and the
OL,20,Fworld leaders who had come to mourn.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
