OL,3,CReporting Rome: Covering the funeral
OL,4,Cof Pope Francis
OL,6,FFrom where I was standing, on the Via
OL,7,Fdella Conciliazione, the people
OL,8,Fattending the open-air Mass were not
OL,9,Fspectators. They were participants.
OL,10,FThey knelt, they prayed, and they took
OL,11,FCommunion.
OL,13,FIn life, Pope Francis had reached out
OL,14,Ffar beyond his comfort zone. He worked
OL,15,Famong the poor in his native
OL,16,FArgentina. He continued to reach out
OL,17,Fto people on the fringes of society,
OL,18,Faround the world, and, particularly in
OL,19,FRome.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
