OL,3,CReporting Rome: Covering the funeral
OL,4,Cof Pope Francis
OL,6,FOn Holy Thursday, he visited the
OL,7,FRegina Coeli prison in Rome. While
OL,8,Funable to celebrate the liturgy of the
OL,9,FLord's Supper and the washing of feet,
OL,10,Fhe greeted inmates personally,
OL,11,Foffering words of encouragement and
OL,12,Fgifts.
OL,14,FThat was the measure of the Pontiff.
OL,16,FWhat will be his legacy? We will have
OL,17,Fa clearer picture of what lies ahead
OL,18,Ffor the Church, after the Conclave.
